{"tid":2455572,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"日本店家「發明」無餡包子　並被日媒稱讚「顛覆常識的發想」！遭台灣網友吐槽：「這就饅頭啊」","createTime":"2021-03-21T08:26:40.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-21T11:27:58.000Z","uid":54930,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"3cef851075b95b7daf93aa1ad0b7d46b1d7d873f","tid":2455572,"uid":54930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T08:26:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.toy-people.com/?p=60471-1&amp;fbclid=IwAR1bmMFMmADYF_z9mjiE-ucYm1KWsTWpdmQMlT077CpUNLyhgv8_szEZwls\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.toy-people.com%2F%3Fp%3D60471-1%26fbclid%3DIwAR1bmMFMmADYF_z9mjiE-ucYm1KWsTWpdmQMlT077CpUNLyhgv8_szEZwls&d=naoD8C4w5OVxKX0KwUpsfXjCBy0DQDxxpn8JrxrWeYE%3D&h=60f125da\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.toy-people.com/?p=60471-1&amp;fbclid=IwAR1bmMFMmADYF_z9mjiE-ucYm1KWsTWpdmQMlT077CpUNLyhgv8_szEZwls</a><br />\n原po: 日刊電電<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不管是中華料理或是台灣小吃，一向都深受日本民眾的喜愛，就好比前一陣子在日本國內流行的珍珠奶茶與雞排，當然平常早餐我們在吃的肉包、菜包也受到日本人的歡迎。<br />\n<br />\n而近日日本媒體《FNN》介紹了一家知名百年老店「井村屋」，研發了完全沒有任何餡料的包子，而此產品推出後不久，就立即在網路上掀起了一波熱門話題，並且在短短兩個月內就銷售一空。日本店家「發明」無餡包子 並被日媒稱讚「顛覆常識的發想」！遭台灣網友吐槽：「這就饅頭啊」日本店家「發明」無餡包子 並被日媒稱讚「顛覆常識的發想」！遭台灣網友吐槽：「這就饅頭啊」<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.toy-people.com/member/16162279941.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.toy-people.com%2Fmember%2F16162279941.jpg&h=4268bccd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.toy-people.com/member/161622803151.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.toy-people.com%2Fmember%2F161622803151.jpg&h=7c909c83&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n井村屋表示，打造「無餡料包子」的構思是源自於在2014年時消費者的請願，希望該店家能夠創造出沒有包任何餡料的包子。基於此，井村屋也開始於2020年嘗試製作無餡料的包子，並且進行試賣，而結果確實成功引起了日本國內民眾的熱烈反應，還因此被《FNN》讚賞是「顛覆常識的發想」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.toy-people.com/member/161622808454.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.toy-people.com%2Fmember%2F161622808454.jpg&h=f178dee7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但我們很清楚，事實上所謂「日本創意發想包子」，就是平時我們都會拿來當早餐吃的饅頭啊！而經過日本《FNN》的報導後，台灣、中國兩國民眾都紛紛吐槽這根本不是什麼獨特發想，而是早就存在的食物，甚至還能夠在各大賣場中看到各式各樣的「創意饅頭」，例如芋頭風味、巧克力口味，或是雙色饅頭&hellip;等等。<br />\n<br />\n而且日本井村屋所「打造」的「無餡料包子」，售價每顆180日圓，換算新台幣大約落在45塊錢左右，對於我們來說真的是相當地昂貴，同樣45元新台幣，在台灣已經可以買到不少顆熱騰騰的饅頭了。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5GV9wKO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5GV9wKO.jpg&h=82bb50fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/O2jip4O.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FO2jip4O.jpg&h=b9634768&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gsccuwt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fgsccuwt.jpg&h=81d2b010&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k1e6yX8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk1e6yX8.jpg&h=a964ab05&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.toy-people.com/?p=60471-1&amp;fbclid=IwAR1bmMFMmADYF_z9mjiE-ucYm1KWsTWpdmQMlT077CpUNLyhgv8_szEZwls\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.toy-people.com%2F%3Fp%3D60471-1%26fbclid%3DIwAR1bmMFMmADYF_z9mjiE-ucYm1KWsTWpdmQMlT077CpUNLyhgv8_szEZwls&d=naoD8C4w5OVxKX0KwUpsfXjCBy0DQDxxpn8JrxrWeYE%3D&h=60f125da\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.toy-people.com/?p=60471-1&amp;fbclid=IwAR1bmMFMmADYF_z9mjiE-ucYm1KWsTWpdmQMlT077CpUNLyhgv8_szEZwls</a><br />\n原po: 日刊電電<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"150043b6192bee0257d6f155bc2295f2048ef01e","tid":2455572,"uid":252784,"like":21,"dislike":7,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T08:33:35.000Z","msg":"又抄人當係自己發明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n中國人真係...sor日本人嚟咁冇嘢了<br />\n真係好有創意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58641d81c10ce8b941a697855b61aa6e9ecc0260","tid":2455572,"uid":25073,"like